                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Port au Prince</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-03-12T17:00:00-04:49">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 12, 1915—5 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Commission has full possession of facts as to situation. Longer stay or further
                    efforts would not accomplish more.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Fort</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
